com.tibbo.aggregate.common.binding

Interface BindingProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBindingProcessor

    public interface BindingProcessor
    BindingProcessor is tightly related to BindingProvider. Its implementation is an engine that executes bindings provider by a BindingProvider.
